    FROM [AppMobilePhones] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[StockQuantity] > 0
    ORDER BY [a].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhoneCategories] AS [a0] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a1] ON [t].[Id] = [a1].[MobilePhoneId]
ORDER BY [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [a0].[Id]

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Brand], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[Description], [a].[DiscountPrice], [a].[ImageUrl], [a].[IsNew], [a].[IsOnSale], [a].[Name], [a].[Price], [a].[SaleEnd], [a].[SaleStart], [a].[StockQuantity]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[ImportCode], [t].[KeeperName], [t].[KeeperPhone], [t].[Note], [t].[SupplierName], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ImportId], [t0].[ImportPrice], [t0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [t0].[MobilePhoneId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Brand], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[Description], [t0].[DiscountPrice], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[IsNew], [t0].[IsOnSale], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[SaleEnd], [t0].[SaleStart], [t0].[StockQuantity], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[ColorHex], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[ImageUrl0], [t0].[MobilePhoneId0], [t0].[StockQuantity0]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[ImportCode], [a].[KeeperName], [a].[KeeperPhone], [a].[Note], [a].[SupplierName]
    FROM [AppImports] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[ImportId], [a0].[ImportPrice], [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [a0].[MobilePhoneId], [a0].[Quantity], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[Brand], [a1].[CategoryId], [a1].[CreationTime], [a1].[Description], [a1].[DiscountPrice], [a1].[ImageUrl], [a1].[IsNew], [a1].[IsOnSale], [a1].[Name], [a1].[Price], [a1].[SaleEnd], [a1].[SaleStart], [a1].[StockQuantity], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[ColorHex], [a2].[ColorName], [a2].[ImageUrl] AS [ImageUrl0], [a2].[MobilePhoneId] AS [MobilePhoneId0], [a2].[StockQuantity] AS [StockQuantity0]
    FROM [AppImportDetails] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhones] AS [a1] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneId] = [a1].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a2] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ImportId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreationTime] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Brand], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[Description], [a].[DiscountPrice], [a].[ImageUrl], [a].[IsNew], [a].[IsOnSale], [a].[Name], [a].[Price], [a].[SaleEnd], [a].[SaleStart], [a].[StockQuantity]

    WHERE [a].[StockQuantity] > 0
    ORDER BY [a].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhoneCategories] AS [a0] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [a0].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Brand], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[Description], [a].[DiscountPrice], [a].[ImageUrl], [a].[IsNew], [a].[IsOnSale], [a].[Name], [a].[Price], [a].[SaleEnd], [a].[SaleStart], [a].[StockQuantity]

) AS [t]

    FROM [AppImports] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[ImportId], [a0].[ImportPrice], [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [a0].[MobilePhoneId], [a0].[Quantity], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[Brand], [a1].[CategoryId], [a1].[CreationTime], [a1].[Description], [a1].[DiscountPrice], [a1].[ImageUrl], [a1].[IsNew], [a1].[IsOnSale], [a1].[Name], [a1].[Price], [a1].[SaleEnd], [a1].[SaleStart], [a1].[StockQuantity], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[ColorHex], [a2].[ColorName], [a2].[ImageUrl] AS [ImageUrl0], [a2].[MobilePhoneId] AS [MobilePhoneId0], [a2].[StockQuantity] AS [StockQuantity0]
    FROM [AppImportDetails] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhones] AS [a1] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneId] = [a1].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a2] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ImportId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[ImportCode], [t].[KeeperName], [t].[KeeperPhone], [t].[Note], [t].[SupplierName], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ImportId], [t0].[ImportPrice], [t0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [t0].[MobilePhoneId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Brand], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[Description], [t0].[DiscountPrice], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[IsNew], [t0].[IsOnSale], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[SaleEnd], [t0].[SaleStart], [t0].[StockQuantity], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[ColorHex], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[ImageUrl0], [t0].[MobilePhoneId0], [t0].[StockQuantity0]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[ImportCode], [a].[KeeperName], [a].[KeeperPhone], [a].[Note], [a].[SupplierName]
    FROM [AppImports] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[ImportId], [a0].[ImportPrice], [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [a0].[MobilePhoneId], [a0].[Quantity], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[Brand], [a1].[CategoryId], [a1].[CreationTime], [a1].[Description], [a1].[DiscountPrice], [a1].[ImageUrl], [a1].[IsNew], [a1].[IsOnSale], [a1].[Name], [a1].[Price], [a1].[SaleEnd], [a1].[SaleStart], [a1].[StockQuantity], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[ColorHex], [a2].[ColorName], [a2].[ImageUrl] AS [ImageUrl0], [a2].[MobilePhoneId] AS [MobilePhoneId0], [a2].[StockQuantity] AS [StockQuantity0]
    FROM [AppImportDetails] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhones] AS [a1] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneId] = [a1].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a2] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ImportId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreationTime] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[ImportCode], [a].[KeeperName], [a].[KeeperPhone], [a].[Note], [a].[SupplierName]
    FROM [AppImports] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[ImportId], [a0].[ImportPrice], [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [a0].[MobilePhoneId], [a0].[Quantity], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[Brand], [a1].[CategoryId], [a1].[CreationTime], [a1].[Description], [a1].[DiscountPrice], [a1].[ImageUrl], [a1].[IsNew], [a1].[IsOnSale], [a1].[Name], [a1].[Price], [a1].[SaleEnd], [a1].[SaleStart], [a1].[StockQuantity], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[ColorHex], [a2].[ColorName], [a2].[ImageUrl] AS [ImageUrl0], [a2].[MobilePhoneId] AS [MobilePhoneId0], [a2].[StockQuantity] AS [StockQuantity0]

    INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhones] AS [a1] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneId] = [a1].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a2] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ImportId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreationTime] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[ImportCode], [a].[KeeperName], [a].[KeeperPhone], [a].[Note], [a].[SupplierName]
    FROM [AppImports] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[ImportId], [a0].[ImportPrice], [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [a0].[MobilePhoneId], [a0].[Quantity], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[Brand], [a1].[CategoryId], [a1].[CreationTime], [a1].[Description], [a1].[DiscountPrice], [a1].[ImageUrl], [a1].[IsNew], [a1].[IsOnSale], [a1].[Name], [a1].[Price], [a1].[SaleEnd], [a1].[SaleStart], [a1].[StockQuantity], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[ColorHex], [a2].[ColorName], [a2].[ImageUrl] AS [ImageUrl0], [a2].[MobilePhoneId] AS [MobilePhoneId0], [a2].[StockQuantity] AS [StockQuantity0]
    FROM [AppImportDetails] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhones] AS [a1] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneId] = [a1].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a2] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ImportId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreationTime] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Brand], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[Description], [a].[DiscountPrice], [a].[ImageUrl], [a].[IsNew], [a].[IsOnSale], [a].[Name], [a].[Price], [a].[SaleEnd], [a].[SaleStart], [a].[StockQuantity]
    FROM [AppMobilePhones] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[StockQuantity] > 0
    ORDER BY [a].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhoneCategories] AS [a0] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a1] ON [t].[Id] = [a1].[MobilePhoneId]
ORDER BY [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [a0].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[Id], [a].[Status], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[TotalAmount]
    FROM [AppOrders] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Name] AS [MobilePhoneName], [a0].[Quantity], [a1].[Price] AS [UnitPrice], [a0].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[OrderId]
    FROM [AppOrderDetails] AS [a0]

INFO  2025-11-14 16:20:14,711 [15   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[ImportCode], [t].[KeeperName], [t].[KeeperPhone], [t].[Note], [t].[SupplierName], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ImportId], [t0].[ImportPrice], [t0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [t0].[MobilePhoneId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Brand], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[Description], [t0].[DiscountPrice], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[IsNew], [t0].[IsOnSale], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[SaleEnd], [t0].[SaleStart], [t0].[StockQuantity], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[ColorHex], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[ImageUrl0], [t0].[MobilePhoneId0], [t0].[StockQuantity0]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[ImportCode], [a].[KeeperName], [a].[KeeperPhone], [a].[Note], [a].[SupplierName]
    FROM [AppImports] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[ImportId], [a0].[ImportPrice], [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [a0].[MobilePhoneId], [a0].[Quantity], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[Brand], [a1].[CategoryId], [a1].[CreationTime], [a1].[Description], [a1].[DiscountPrice], [a1].[ImageUrl], [a1].[IsNew], [a1].[IsOnSale], [a1].[Name], [a1].[Price], [a1].[SaleEnd], [a1].[SaleStart], [a1].[StockQuantity], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[ColorHex], [a2].[ColorName], [a2].[ImageUrl] AS [ImageUrl0], [a2].[MobilePhoneId] AS [MobilePhoneId0], [a2].[StockQuantity] AS [StockQuantity0]
    FROM [AppImportDetails] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhones] AS [a1] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneId] = [a1].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a2] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ImportId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreationTime] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[ImportCode], [t].[KeeperName], [t].[KeeperPhone], [t].[Note], [t].[SupplierName], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ImportId], [t0].[ImportPrice], [t0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [t0].[MobilePhoneId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Brand], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[Description], [t0].[DiscountPrice], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[IsNew], [t0].[IsOnSale], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[SaleEnd], [t0].[SaleStart], [t0].[StockQuantity], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[ColorHex], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[ImageUrl0], [t0].[MobilePhoneId0], [t0].[StockQuantity0]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[ImportCode], [a].[KeeperName], [a].[KeeperPhone], [a].[Note], [a].[SupplierName]
    FROM [AppImports] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[ImportId], [a0].[ImportPrice], [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId], [a0].[MobilePhoneId], [a0].[Quantity], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[Brand], [a1].[CategoryId], [a1].[CreationTime], [a1].[Description], [a1].[DiscountPrice], [a1].[ImageUrl], [a1].[IsNew], [a1].[IsOnSale], [a1].[Name], [a1].[Price], [a1].[SaleEnd], [a1].[SaleStart], [a1].[StockQuantity], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[ColorHex], [a2].[ColorName], [a2].[ImageUrl] AS [ImageUrl0], [a2].[MobilePhoneId] AS [MobilePhoneId0], [a2].[StockQuantity] AS [StockQuantity0]
    FROM [AppImportDetails] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [AppMobilePhones] AS [a1] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneId] = [a1].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [AppMobilePhoneColors] AS [a2] ON [a0].[MobilePhoneColorId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ImportId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreationTime] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]
